title: La Maison Du Moustache Frituur De Snor
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Fast food, Take-out, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Deep-fry french fries, sandwiches, cakes, coffee, made-in-house hot sauces, lots of ready-made snacks and made-in-house fresh snacks, including vegan asparagus and mushroom croquettes, onion rings and others. Daily specials freshly made to order.
